Push the Code to Git & GitHub Repository
-----------------------------------------

1) Create local git repository for your project
    git init   ---. Create an Empty git repository (Local repository)

2) Connect your local git(local rep) with Github (global)
     git remote add origin https://github.com/anbu3474/Seleniumframework.git

3) Before doing commit first time we need to execute these below commands
     git config --global user.name "anbu3474"
     git config --global user.email "anbu3474@gmail.com"

4)
     git status (check the status of the files commited /notcommited
     git add -A (Add all the files to staging area)
     git commit -m  "first commit" ( Commit the code into git repository( local rep)
5) Push the code form git --> github repository
     git push -u origin master












